SOURCE FIELDS
    REQUIRED desc
END SOURCE FIELDS

FIELD desc TYPE TEXT
    SCOPE SOURCE
END FIELD

ITEM FIELDS
    REQUIRED text, note, code
END ITEM FIELDS

FIELD text TYPE QUOTATION
    SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD

FIELD note TYPE MEMO
    SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD

FIELD code TYPE CODE
    SCOPE ITEM
END FIELD


ONTOLOGY FIELDS
    REQUIRED topic
END ONTOLOGY FIELDS

FIELD topic TYPE ENUMERATED
    SCOPE ONTOLOGY
    VALUES
        [1] usability: Usability of the system
        [2] reliability: Reliability over time
    END VALUES
END FIELD